import React from 'react'
import { Card } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Data = () => (
  <Card.Group className="Card">
    <Card>
      <Card.Content>
        <Card.Header>Donations</Card.Header>
        <Card.Description>
          $10000
        </Card.Description>
      </Card.Content>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <Card.Content>
        <Card.Header content='Doctors and Health Workers' />
        <Card.Description content='1500' />
      </Card.Content>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <Card.Content
        header='Patients'
        description='2000'
      />
    </Card>
  </Card.Group>
)

export default Data;
